            <p>Focus on 3 major areas:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>selection of renal replacement modality</li>
              <li> management of glycaemic control </li>
              <li> management and prevention of cardiovascular comorbidity </li>
          </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
       <!-- Fine Testo Scope Guidelines -->

    <div class="p-box pb-2 pb-lg-8">
